name: Women's Owl Tee
description:
These shirts are created with block prints and fabric paint. Each block was hand carved and then stamped onto the tee. Each one will appear different because of the varying pressure and amount of screenprinting ink/paint on each block.

ABOUT THE SHIRT:
The shirt is soft, slate (dark gray), v-neck, 100% cotton, American Apparel brand

SIZES:
UNISEX/women's S/M/L/XL

WASHING:
Wash it all you want (or don't want) the fabric paint is permanent. Just make sure you smile in it (looks better)

name: Women's Dragon Tee on American Apparel
description:
This shirt was made using block prints I carved. 

The story about the dragon goes:

This dragon has been trapped on the outside of this take out box for thousands of years (like through a dynasty or 2). He has bounced from box to box and finally has been freed. Take him with you and show him the world. He loves jungle gyms and has a major sweet tooth. He has had his fill of #49 and General Tsao's chicken. SO get him a cupcake and take him to the park.

NOTE: Each shirt is hand crafted by me (drawn, printed, carved, and ironed!).

SIZE: American Apparel (small, medium, large, xlarge)
